➜25万元选中型瓦罐车，底盘变高轮眉加大，一汽-大众新CC上市
http://www.sohu.com/a/437063651_99994080	46344
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/5ef395bf4799417c890180df7d591593.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/ab029b3e0ace417d80b80c4bd65d0f2f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/14fbb7d5853146d386b97a4010988fe3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
